.SH NAME
pstr-compose-ai - Generate a draft with AI


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpstr compose ai [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate a draft with a configured AI template and save or send it as a normal Postero message.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--account\fP=""
	account name or email to send from

.PP
\fB--attach\fP=[]
	file path to attach; can be specified multiple times

.PP
\fB--bcc\fP=[]
	bcc recipient addresses

.PP
\fB--body\fP=""
	body hint passed to the template

.PP
\fB--cc\fP=[]
	cc recipient addresses

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for ai

.PP
\fB--instruction\fP=""
	high-level drafting instruction for the template

.PP
\fB--send\fP[=false]
	send immediately instead of saving a draft

.PP
\fB--subject\fP=""
	subject hint passed to the template

.PP
\fB--template\fP=""
	ai template name from config

.PP
\fB--to\fP=[]
	recipient addresses

.PP
\fB--var\fP=[]
	additional template variables as key=value


